<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/128/point/c> legal:pointHasKey "c" .
<$http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2020/11/pasal/128/point/c> legal:pointHasText ". Penyertaan modal negara, dan" .
